{"title_page": "HaSeul", "text_new": "{{for|the singer|Loona (band)}}\n{{Infobox album\n| name         = HaSeul\n| cover        = Haseul_cover.png\n| alt          = \n| type         = Single Album\n| artist       = [[Loona (band)|Loona]]\n| language     = [[Korean language|Korean]]\n| released     = December 15, 2016\n| recorded     = \n| studio       = \n| venue        = \n| genre        = [[Pop music|Pop, Ballad]]\n| length       = 6:35\n| label        = {{hlist|[[Blockberry Creative]]|[[CJ E&M]]}}\n| composer     = \n| lyricist     = \n| producer     = \n| prev_title   = [[HyunJin (single)|HyunJin]]\n| prev_year    = 2016\n| next_title   = [[YeoJin (single)|YeoJin]]\n| next_year    = 2017\n| misc         = {{External music video|type=single|{{YouTube|6a4BWpBJppI|\"Let Me In\"}}<br>{{YouTube|WX-lpEnIQQk|\"The Carol\"}}}}\n}}\n\n'''''HaSeul''''' (or '''''LOO\u03a0\u0394 & HaSeul''''') is the third [[single album]] from [[South Korea]]n [[girl group]] [[Loona (band)|Loona]]'s pre-debut project. It was released on December 15, 2016, by [[Polaris Entertainment|Blockberry Creative]] and distributed by [[CJ E&M]].<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.sedaily.com/NewsView/1L59776DSW/|title=\uac78\uadf8\ub8f9 \uc774\ub2ec\uc758 \uc18c\ub140 '\ud558\uc2ac', \uc194\ub85c\uace1 \u2018\uc18c\ub144,\uc18c\ub140\u2019 \ubca0\uc77c \ubc97\uc5c8\ub2e4...'\ube14\ub85d\ubc84\uc2a4\ud130 \ud2b8\ub799'|publisher=SE Daily|language=ko}}</ref> It introduces member HaSeul and contains two tracks, her solo \"Let Me In\", and a Christmas collaboration song between her, HeeJin and HyunJin, titled \"The Carol\". Music Videos for both songs were released simultaneously on December 15.Haseul is my papi and i give her lap dances on the weekend\n\n==Track listing==\n{{Track listing\n| extra_column    = Arrangement\n\n| title1          = Let Me In (\uc18c\ub144, \uc18c\ub140)\n| note1           = HaSeul solo\n| length1         = 3:08\n| lyrics1         = Oreo\n| music1          = Oreo\n| extra1         